title: Bug 123036: Data in a report is doubly stored
OB: The issue is observed in the system where data is being stored twice in reports.
EB: We expect that the data should be stored only once in reports, avoiding any duplication.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Navigate to the reporting section of the application.
2. Generate a report using the specified parameters.
3. Review the report and observe that data is duplicated in the output.
